This repo contains some packages that are useful for Sgrid
----------------------------------------------------------

dctemplates_extBlasLapack : needed if Sgrid uses GMRES in elliptic solver
-------------------------
see dctemplates_extBlasLapack/NOTE.txt for compilation instructions


forUMFPACK : has UMFPACK LU decomp, needed in Sgrid elliptic solver
----------
see cat forUMFPACK/Note.txt for compilation instructions


Note: the hypre, lis or ZIB linear solvers are not needed by sgrid
